metadata.name: Mpepe #1
metadata.description: Mpepes, aka Mondrian Pepes - where Pepe the frog meets Piet Mondrian in the most unexpected and hilarious way possible, featuring the iconic green amphibian in the bold, geometric style of the Dutch master himself. Own a piece of internet history with an artistic twist. No roadmap or promises. All for the culture. Pepes are forever !!
